name: Bichu
description:
Si es cierto que por comer mucho pollo con hormonas te crecen los man-boobs, puede ser que con ésta camisa te crezcan los músculos...entre otras cosas.
Esta edición de "Bichú" está impresa en una camisa "heather" suuuuuuper suavecita!
This shirt features our awesome hormone-pumped chicken. "Bichú" litteraly means "big dick", but it also means "awesome" and it's a pun of a local chicken factory name! Cock-a-doodle-do, mofo!
This "Bichú" edition is printed on a super soft "heather" tshirt!

name: Beyakin
description:
Si las mujeres dan vueltas alrededor de tu vida como en esta camisa, de seguro eres un beyakin!
If women float around you like in this shirt, then "Beyakin" is for you. Beyakin literally means "horny guy", you naughty boy, you!

name: Puñata
description:
Si las piñatas hablaran gritarían esto! Camisa color frambuesa piragua, 100% algodón suavecito
If piñatas could talk, they'd scream "PUÑATA!" which is a play on the boricua favorite cuss word: "PUÑETA!". Stay classy!

name: Trisom
description:
Tres monjitas haciendo un trisom con un galón de leche! Seems legit!
Three nuns having a threesome with a gallon of milk... seems legit! (Design is a pun/parody of a famous milk company!)

name: Cock Soccer
description:
Saca el gallito deportivo en tí!...riiiiight! Esta camisa está disponible para chicos y para chicas!
For all those cocky sport lovers out there! Shirt available in guys & girl styles.

name: Moderfoca
description:
¿Qué le dijo el hijo foca a su madre foca? “Foc you!” Como te imaginarás, la madre foca le metió sendo bofetón a su hijo, pa’ que no fuese tan hijo de foca.
"Moderfoca" sounds like "motherfucker" but it literally translates to "Mother Seal". Wow, we're such smartasses.

name: Muerte al Reggaetón
description:
Todo movimiento tiene seguidores y opositores. Hemos respondido a tus plegarias. 3 mil billones de copias, obligao!
Proudly proclaim "Death to Reggaetón" with this shirt. Shirt available only for hardcore rockers and/or people that appreciate good music.

name: Cachete
description:
Este es tu uniforme oficial para las fiestas, get-togethers o cualquier otra ocasión donde vayas a cachetear. Y como sabemos que el cacheteo es un estilo de vida, sabemos que esta será una camisa perfecta para todos los días!
This epic shirt says "I'm just here to freeload" in puertorican slang. Great for parties or everyday life, since we are all about getting stuff for free.

name: Wabbatman
description:
Nuestra mascota Wabba, merodea en la noche vigilando que todo ciudadano tenga comida en su casa...para luego ella comérsela. Na na na na na na na na Wabbatman!
Wabba, our fat bunny mascot, prowls the night making sure every citizen's fridge is stocked with food...so she can eat it all. A silent glutton. A watchful devourer. A Fat Knight.

name: Bochin-Che
description:
Divisivamente odiada y amada, La reina del bochinche...todo un enigma revolucionario! No importa si celebras la muerte de La Comay o su vida, esta camisa troliará a todos por igual!
As seen on The Daily Show- La Comay was Puerto Rico's gossip revolutionary. Whether you celebrate La Comay's life or death, this shirt is still trolling everyone.

name: TV
description:
Para un mundo más feliz. Garantizado!
The solution for a better world. Shirt says: "Less Soap Operas, More Cartoons"

name: Wabba Sticker
description:
Wabba es la mascota oficial de Tripleta! Una coneja adorable, apretujable, hambrienta y mortífera. Rockea tu amor por Wabba con estos stickers super pro! Hechos en vinyl a prueba de agua, sol, lluvia y dragones (probablemente). Tamaño aprox. 3"x4"
Wabba is Tripleta's official mascot. Cute, hungry and deadly, Wabba is always adorably misleading. Show your Wabba love with these high quality vinyl stickers. UV coated, waterproof and dragon-proof (probaby). Aprox. size 3"x4"

name: Burbu Wars
description:
Aquí nadie se va a dormir, porque estámos rabiosos! Oh sí, Oh sí!
This epic shirt features a Tripleta spin on 90's childhood. Super Soakers and Boricua Children's TV favorites Burbujita and Bolillo. Our childhood is piiiiiissed!

name: Tripletista Hoodie
description:
Keep warm and rock your cool with this unisex zip hoodie featuring 3 mischevous Wabbas trying to climb up your arm! They probably want to steal your food. Made from premium, super soft, lightweight fleece offering a slim fit and quality construction. Charcoal gray.
Protégete del "sereno" con este hoodie unisex super calientito, incluye a 3 Wabbas traviesas tratando de subir por tu brazo (probablemente para robar tu comida). Hecha de lana super premium, estos jackets ofrecen un estilo "slim" ajustadito y fashon. Color charcoal gray.

name: Gogo Inc.
description:
Pigeons: Mobile shit factories. Discover the inner workings of pigeons in this epic shirt. Featuring our pet pigeon, Gogo.
Paloma: Fábrica de caca ambulante. Héchale un vistazo en detalle a los misterios palomosos con esta camisa super cool. Con la actuación estelar de nuestra paloma Gogó.

name: Tripleta Sport
description:
This fresh shirt goes with anything, but especially your torso. Featuring 100% ringspun cotton and tagless size label for extra comfort.
Esta camisa combina con todo, pero especialmente con tu torso. Hecha con 100% algodón suavecito y con el size impreso para máxima comodidad.

name: Simple Wabba
description:
Essential. Classy. Hungry. Wabba is our official mascot. A cute obese bunny that will eat it's way into your life... and heart.
Esencial. Elegante. Hambrienta. Wabba es nuestra mascota oficial. Una coneja obesamente cute que devorará su camino hacia tu vida... y tu corazón.

name: Wabba Cap Gray
description:
Snapback trucker mesh cap featuring Wabba, our official mascot. Gray version.
Gorra "snapback" estilo mesh con diseño de nuestra mascota Wabba. Versión gris.

name: Wabba Cap Black
description:
Snapback trucker mesh cap featuring Wabba, our official mascot. Black version.
Gorra "snapback" estilo mesh con diseño de nuestra mascota Wabba. Versión negra.

name: Crapi
description:
Crapi es el Mr.Hanky boricua. Deja que su felicidad embarre todos los días de tu vida con esta gorra épica!
Fresh trucker snapback featuring "Crapi", the boricua Mr.Hanky that likes to hang out in very specific crappy department stores.

name: Tripleta Bones Sticker
description:
Demuestra tu amor Tripletoso con estos stickers super pro! Hechos en vinyl a prueba de agua, sol, lluvia y dragones (probablemente).
Show your Tripleta love with these high quality vinyl stickers. UV coated, waterproof and dragon-proof (probaby).

name: Glow Bones
description:
Camisa color berenjena espacial. Logo de Tripleta™ es color blanco, y cuando apagas las luces brilla en la oscuridad! Osom.
Our standard 100% cotton shirt featuring Tripleta's awesome "Bones" logo. Printed with special glow in the dark ink! Badass.

name: Y-Rex
description:
Éste dinosaurio lleva arrasando desde la época del Super Nintendo. Ya era hora de que evolucionara. Yo shi sé quien es, y tu?
This is what happens when Yoshi eats bad mushrooms.

name: Goth Bless You
description:
Bienvenidos a la iglesia del rock. OH MAI GOTH!
Welcome to the church of rock. OH MY GOTH!!

name: Cafre Yaulitza
description:
Porque lo cafre es más boricua que el café, Tripleta presenta un tributo a las chancletas metedeos, dubis, rolos, uñas acrílicas, chichos envueltos en leggins, tatuajes tecatos y cejas hechas con Sharpie. Mmmmm!
"Cafre" is boricua for "ghetto". And nothing is more ghetto OR boricua than flip flops, dubis, rollers, acrylic nails and leggins paired with some sexy love handles. Mmmmm!

Design is also a play on words, since "Cafre" sounds like "Café", and this is a parody of a famous puertorrican coffee mascot!

name: Saving Point #1
description:
Created with love by the artistic husband and wife team of Tripleta Chefs Rangely García and Samuel Figueroa; "Saving Point" is an action/adventure/comedy story set in a fantasy world that breathes classic RPG game elements.
In this issue: An ancient statuette containing the power of the world's oldest enemy has been stolen! Follow Bolaf and his band of underdogs as they embark on a journey that will change their lives...in every sense of the word!
24 pages, full color. English.

name: Saving Point #2
description:
Created with love by the artistic husband and wife team of Tripleta Chefs Rangely García and Samuel Figueroa; "Saving Point" is an action/adventure/comedy story set in a fantasy world that breathes classic RPG game elements.
In this issue: Bolaf and his team are left dragging a heavy problem as Yessia has been turned into stone! Will they be able to return to the village and claim their loot before the monsters show up?
24 pages, full color. English.

name: Bota
description:
Porque sean verdes, azules o rojos, todos han demostrado ser brown por dentro, cuando votes, bota los partidos! "Bota" está disponible en sizes de adultos y sizes de "youth" que pueden ser utilizados por niños o muchachas flaquitas. Si estás chichosa, pide un size más grande.
This shirt features Puerto Rico's mayor political parties' insignias desecrated Tripleta-style! Politics have never been so offensive and fun! Shirt is available in adult and youth sizes. Youth sizes fit sassy children and skinny gals. Rock on!

name: Gafas que Ciegan
description:
Si ves el mundo a través de un lente político y fanático, te quedarás ciego. En Tripleta™ queremos que uses tu cerebro, sigue tu ideal pero nunca te fanatizes (a menos que te fanatizes con nosotros, ahí está cool)
Looking at the world through a political lens will leave you blind. This shirt features glasses with Puerto Rico's major political parties in each lens. The caption reads: "Glasses that Blind"

name: Psycho
description:
Psycho, Psycho! Si no tiene cuchillita no es Psycho de verdad! Los de la mascarita, los que dicen Tripleta™! No te dejes engañar! Esta nueva y mejorada versión de "Psycho" está impresa en camisas 100% algodón super soft y fashion, tienen el diseño más grande y con más sangre y además viene para chicos y chicas (mientras duren!)
A parody of a classic boricua ice cream brand. Yeah, cuz nobody suspects serial psycho killers in ice cream trucks, right?

name: Cangri
description:
Nacido y criado en el underground de las arenas de Piñones, aquí llegó el cangrejo más cangri pa' quedarse con el canto. "Cangri" está disponible en sizes de adultos y sizes de "youth" que pueden ser utilizados por niños o muchachas flaquitas. Si estás chichosa, pide un size más grande.
"Cangri" is a boricua street slang that means "awesome". It also sounds a whole lot like "cangrejo"...which means "crab". C'mon, don't be so crabby! Hella' cute.
Shirt is available in adult and youth sizes. Youth sizes fit sassy children and skinny gals. Rock on!
